stateDiagram-v2
    %% ワークフローフェーズ遷移（regression_test追加後）

    [*] --> idle: タスクなし

    idle --> research: workflow_start

    research --> requirements: workflow_next
    requirements --> parallel_analysis: workflow_next
    parallel_analysis --> parallel_design: 全サブフェーズ完了

    parallel_design --> design_review: 全サブフェーズ完了
    design_review --> test_design: workflow_approve design

    test_design --> test_impl: workflow_next
    test_impl --> implementation: workflow_next
    implementation --> refactoring: workflow_next
    refactoring --> parallel_quality: workflow_next

    parallel_quality --> testing: 全サブフェーズ完了

    %% ★ regression_test フェーズの追加
    testing --> regression_test: workflow_next
    regression_test --> parallel_verification: 全テストパス

    note right of regression_test
        リグレッションテスト失敗時は
        次フェーズに進めない
    end note

    parallel_verification --> docs_update: 全サブフェーズ完了
    docs_update --> commit: workflow_next
    commit --> push: workflow_next
    push --> ci_verification: workflow_next
    ci_verification --> deploy: workflow_next
    deploy --> completed: workflow_next

    completed --> [*]: タスク完了

    %% リセット
    research --> research: workflow_reset
    requirements --> research: workflow_reset
    parallel_analysis --> research: workflow_reset
    parallel_design --> research: workflow_reset
    design_review --> research: workflow_reset
    test_design --> research: workflow_reset
    test_impl --> research: workflow_reset
    implementation --> research: workflow_reset
    refactoring --> research: workflow_reset
    parallel_quality --> research: workflow_reset
    testing --> research: workflow_reset
    regression_test --> research: workflow_reset
    parallel_verification --> research: workflow_reset
